Distribution map of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Sotoodeh" authorityYear="2022" box="[456,580,1024,1045]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Scrophulariaceae" genus="Verbascum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="3" pageNumber="38" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="urumiense">
